org.efaps.admin.access

Class AccessKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.efaps.admin.access.AccessKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Indexed
public final class AccessKey
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Used as a key to store the results of a Query related to access in a map.
    Uses:
    • Id of the type from the related Instance
    • Id of object from the related Instance
    • Id of the person the result belongs to
    • Id of the company the result belongs to
    • AccessType (e.g. CREATE, CHECKIN) the result belongs to
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    The eFaps Team
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
